# Telangana RURAL

ANALYSIS BASED ON DATA FROM GOVERNMENT SCHOOLS. 9 OUT OF 9 DISTRICTS
Data is not presented where sample size is insufficient.

## School observations

In each sampled village, the largest government school with primary sections is visited on the day of the survey. Information about schools in this report is based on these visits.

### Table 14: Trends over time
Number of schools visited 2010, 2012, 2014 and 2016

| Type of school | 2010 | 2012 | 2014 | 2016 |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Primary schools (Std I-IV/V) | 200 | 213 | 203 | 210 |
| Upper primary schools (Std I-VII/VIII) | 58 | 49 | 61 | 54 |
| Total schools visited | 258 | 262 | 264 | 264 |

